BonfyrePipeline — unified single-process pipeline

Usage:
  bonfyre-pipeline run <input> --out DIR [--type TYPE] [--artifacts DIR]
      [--key KEY] [--key-file F] [--tier TIER]

Audio files (.wav/.mp3/.m4a/.flac/.ogg or --type audio):
  Runs transcript pipeline: transcribe → clean → brief → proof → tag → offer → pack

Other types:
  Runs data pipeline: gate → ingest → index → compress → meter → stitch → ledger
